{{Lunisolar September}} 
'''September 28''' is the 28th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  and its day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year /{{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1331|ja|1331|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The exiled Emperor {{ill|Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  took refuge in Kasagiyama; the Kamakura shogunate then turned against {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , and the emperor was captured the following day.
* {{ill|Chōroku|ja|長禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1457|ja|1457|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The era name was changed from {{ill|Kōsei|ja|康正|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  to {{ill|Chōroku|ja|長禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1629|ja|1629|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iefusa|ja|徳川頼房|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  completed the construction of a garden (later known as {{ill|Kōrakuen|ja|後楽園|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) at his Mito domain villa in Koishikawa.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1757|ja|1757|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ōtsuki Genzawa|ja|大槻玄沢|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a rangaku scholar († {{ill|1827|ja|1827|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1809|ja|1809|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Shimazu Nariakira|ja|島津斉彬|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , lord of the Satsuma Domain († {{ill|1858|ja|1858|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1864|ja|1864|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yokogawa Minosuke|ja|横河民輔|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an architect and entrepreneur († {{ill|1945|ja|1945|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1867|ja|1867|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 25|ja|10月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Hiranuma Kiichirō|ja|平沼騏一郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , who later served as Prime Minister for the 35th time († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Meiō|ja|明応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1500|ja|1500|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Gotomonomine|ja|後土御門天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 103rd emperor (* {{ill|1442|ja|1442|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

