{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:17, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月廿八|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 28일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 28''' is the 28th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and its day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year /{{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1331|ja|1331|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The exiled Emperor {{ill|Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} took refuge in Kasagiyama; the Kamakura shogunate then turned against {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , and the emperor was captured the following day. * {{ill|Chōroku|ja|長禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1457|ja|1457|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The era name was changed from {{ill|Kōsei|ja|康正|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to {{ill|Chōroku|ja|長禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iefusa|ja|徳川頼房|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} completed the construction of a garden (later known as {{ill|Kōrakuen|ja|後楽園|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) at his Mito domain villa in Koishikawa. == Births == * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1757|ja|1757|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Ōtsuki Genzawa|ja|大槻玄沢|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a rangaku scholar († {{ill|1827|ja|1827|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1809|ja|1809|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Shimazu Nariakira|ja|島津斉彬|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , lord of the Satsuma Domain († {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Yokogawa Minosuke|ja|横河民輔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , an architect and entrepreneur († {{ill|1945|ja|1945|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 25|ja|10月25日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Hiranuma Kiichirō|ja|平沼騏一郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , who later served as Prime Minister for the 35th time († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Meiō|ja|明応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 9th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1500|ja|1500|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Gotomonomine|ja|後土御門天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 103rd emperor (* {{ill|1442|ja|1442|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
