|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1629|qq=}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 13|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iefusa|ja|徳川頼房|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iefusa|qq=}} completed the construction of a garden (later known as {{ill|Kōrakuen|ja|後楽園|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōrakuen|qq=}} ) at his Mito domain villa in Koishikawa. == Births == * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōreki|qq=}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1757|ja|1757|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1757|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 9|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Ōtsuki Genzawa|ja|大槻玄沢|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtsuki Genzawa|qq=}} , a rangaku scholar († {{ill|1827|ja|1827|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1827|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunka (era)|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1809|ja|1809|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1809|qq=}} {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 5|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Shimazu Nariakira|ja|島津斉彬|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimazu Nariakira|qq=}} , lord of the Satsuma Domain († {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genji|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1864|qq=}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 28|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Yokogawa Minosuke|ja|横河民輔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokogawa Minosuke|qq=}} , an architect and entrepreneur († {{ill|1945|ja|1945|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1945|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1867|qq=}} {{ill|October 25|ja|10月25日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 25|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Hiranuma Kiichirō|ja|平沼騏一郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiranuma Kiichirō|qq=}} , who late