== Events == * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gentoku|qq=}} 3rd year /{{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkō|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1331|ja|1331|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1331|qq=}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 30|qq=}} ） – The exiled Emperor {{ill|Godaigo|ja|後醍醐天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Godaigo|qq=}} took refuge in Kasagiyama; the Kamakura shogunate then turned against {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}} , and the emperor was captured the following day. * {{ill|Chōroku|ja|長禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōroku|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1457|ja|1457|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1457|qq=}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 16|qq=}} ） – The era name was changed from {{ill|Kōsei|ja|康正|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōsei|qq=}} to {{ill|Chōroku|ja|長禄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōroku|qq=}} . * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1629|qq=}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 13|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iefusa|ja|徳川頼房|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iefusa|qq=}} completed the construction of a garden (later known as {{ill|Kōrakuen|ja|後楽園|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōrakuen|qq=}} ) at his Mito domain villa in Koishikawa. == Births == * {{ill|Hōreki|1=Hōreki|2=ja|3=宝暦|ja|Hōreki|1=Hōreki|2=ja|3=宝暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōreki|qq=}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1757|ja|1757|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1757|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 9|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Ōtsuki Genzawa|ja|大槻玄沢|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtsuki Genzawa|qq=}} , a rangaku scholar († {{ill|1827|ja|1827|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1827|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunka (era)|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1809|ja|1809|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1809|qq=}} {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 5|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Shimazu Nariakira|ja|島津斉彬|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimazu Nariakira|qq=}} , lord of the Satsuma Domain († {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genji|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1864|qq=}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 28|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Yokogawa Minosuke|ja|横河民輔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokogawa Minosuke|qq=}} , an architect and entrepreneur († {{ill|1945|ja|1945|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1945|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1867|qq=}} {{ill|October 25|ja|10月25日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 25|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Hiranuma Kiichirō|ja|平沼騏一郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiranuma Kiichirō|qq=}} , who later served as Prime Minister for the 35th time († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1952|qq=}} ).
