e|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Genji era|Genji]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1864|qq=}} [[:en:October 28|October 28]] ） – {{ill|Yokogawa Minosuke|ja|横河民輔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokogawa Minosuke|qq=}} , an architect and entrepreneur († {{ill|1945|ja|1945|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1945|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1867|ja|1867|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1867|qq=}} [[:en:October 25|October 25]] ） – [[:en:Hiranuma Kiichirō|Hiranuma Kiichirō]] , who later served as Prime Minister for the 35th time († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1952|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Meiō|Meiō]] 9th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1500|ja|1500|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1500|qq=}} [[:en:October 21|October 21]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Go-Tsuchimikado|Gotomonomine]] , the 103rd emperor (* {{ill|1442|ja|1442|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1442|qq=}} ).
