== Events == * [[:en:Gentoku|Gentoku]] 3rd year /[[:en:Genkō (1331–1334)|Genkō]] 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1331|1331]] [[:en:October 30|October 30]] ） – The exiled Emperor [[:en:Emperor Go-Daigo|Godaigo]] took refuge in Kasagiyama; the Kamakura shogunate then turned against {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} , and the emperor was captured the following day. * [[:en:Chōroku|Chōroku]] 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1457|1457]] [[:en:October 16|October 16]] ） – The era name was changed from [[:en:Kōshō|Kōsei]] to [[:en:Chōroku|Chōroku]] . * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 6th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1629|1629]] [[:en:November 13|November 13]] ） – [[:en:Tokugawa Yorifusa|Tokugawa Iefusa]] completed the construction of a garden (later known as [[:en:Kōraku-en|Kōrakuen]] ) at his Mito domain villa in Koishikawa. == Births == * [[:en:Hōreki|Hōreki]] 7th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1757|ja|1757|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1757|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 9|November 9]] ） – {{ill|Ōtsuki Genzawa|ja|大槻玄沢|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtsuki Genzawa|qq=}} , a rangaku scholar († {{ill|1827|ja|1827|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1827|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ). * [[:en:Bunka|Bunka]] 6th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1809|ja|1809|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1809|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 5|November 5]] ） – [[:en:Shimazu Nariakira|Shimazu Nariakira]] , lord of the Satsuma Domain († {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ). * [[:en:Genji era|Genji]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1864|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 28|October 28]] ） – {{ill|Yokogawa Minosuke|ja|横河民輔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokogawa Minosuke|qq=}} , an architect and entrepreneur († {{ill|1945|ja|1945|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1945|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1867|ja|1867|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1867|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:October 25|October 25]] ） – [[:en:Hiranuma Kiichirō|Hiranuma Kiichirō]] , who later served as Prime Minister for the 35th time († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1952|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Meiō|Meiō]] 9th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1500|1500]] [[:en:October 21|October 21]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Go-Tsuchimikado|Gotomonomine]] , the 103rd emperor (* [[:en:1442|1442]] ).
