945|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1945|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1867|ja|1867|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1867|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:October 25|October 25]] ） – [[:en:Hiranuma Kiichirō|Hiranuma Kiichirō]] , who later served as Prime Minister for the 35th time († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1952|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Meiō|Meiō]] 9th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1500|1500]] [[:en:October 21|October 21]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Go-Tsuchimikado|Gotomonomine]] , the 103rd emperor (* [[:en:1442|1442]] ).
